   <!-- nicher PARAGRAPH e BOLD, IRALIC, UNDERLINE kora hoyeche -->

   <p> Paragraphs are the <b>building blocks of papers.</b> Many students define paragraphs in <i>terms of length:</i> <u>a paragraph is a group of at least five sentences,</u> a paragraph is half a page long, etc. In reality, though, the <b>unity and coherence </b> of ideas among sentences is what <i><u> constitutes a paragraph.</u></i></p>


